title: Ubehage's FileComparer v1.1
description:
Ubehage's FileComparer v1.1
---------------------------

This is a new small tool that I made for my own needs.
And then I tweaked it a little bit, to be able to publish it :)

This application will compare 2 given files, and tell you if the files are identical or not.


Screenshots:  
http://i.imgur.com/mcnCR4i.jpg  
http://i.imgur.com/nnHmcow.jpg  
http://i.imgur.com/1ZdWe1f.jpg  
http://i.imgur.com/tet88ah.jpg


Fixes in this release:
- Improved memory-management.
- Data-analysis runs a little faster now.
- Saving results is MUCH faster.



/Ubehage
